<!DOCTYPE html>

<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />

    <title>Nobody Told Me About id</title>
    <meta name="description" content="A Build Engine-style gameplay mod for UZDoom" />

    <link rel="canonical" href="https://cantsleep.cc/ntmai" />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/x-icon" href="/assets/ico/ntmai.ico" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/assets/css/ntmai.css" />

    <meta http-equiv="Content-Language" content="en" />
    <meta name="robots" content="index, follow" />

    <meta property="og:title" content="Nobody Told Me About id" />
    <meta property="og:description" content="A Build Engine-style gameplay mod for UZDoom" />
    <meta property="og:url" content="https://cantsleep.cc/ntmai" />
    <meta property="og:type" content="profile" />

    <link rel="preload" href="/assets/img/ntmai_logo.png" as="image" />
    <link rel="preload" href="/assets/img/ntmai_banner.png" as="image" />

    {% block head %}{% endblock head %}

    <script defer src="https://umami.schwung.us/script.js"
        data-website-id="40a0ba16-61a8-407b-a876-1b42949e761c"></script>
    <script defer src="/assets/js/modal.js"></script>
    <script defer src="/assets/js/footer.js"></script>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="body">
        <header><img src="/assets/img/ntmai_banner.png" /></header>

        <main>
            <div class="cool">
                <img src="/assets/img/ntmai_logo.png" alt="Nobody Told Me About id" />
                <p><sub>Build-Engine style gameplay mod for UZDoom</sub></p>
                <br>
                <p>[
                    <a href="https://github.com/localins/NTMAi">GitHub</a>
                    |
                    <a href="https://github.com/localins/NTMAi/releases/latest">Download</a>* |
                    <a href="https://discord.gg/RxWqRb2uQB">Discord</a>
                    ]<br>
                    <sub>*Requires UZDoom 4.14.3 or newer and a copy of Doom.</sub>
                </p>
            </div>
            <br>

            <div class="hr"></div>
            <br>

            <div class="gallery">
                <img src="/assets/img/ntmai_screen1.png" class="modal" alt="MAYhem 2019<br>MAP01: Spiteful Hall" />
                <img src="/assets/img/ntmai_screen2.png" class="modal" alt="AUGER;ZENITH<br>MAP01: Glass Messiah" />
                <img src="/assets/img/ntmai_screen3.png" class="modal" alt="Scythe 2<br>MAP32: Super Secret" />
                <img src="/assets/img/ntmai_screen4.png" class="modal" alt="Doom<br>E3M8: Dis" />
            </div>
            <br>

            <div class="hr"></div>
            <br>

            <div class="profile">
                <div>
                    <h1>FROM ANOTHER UNIVERSE</h1>
                    <p>
                        <b>Nobody Told Me About id</b> is a love letter from Doom fans to the iconic trinity of Build
                        Engine games; Duke Nukem 3D, Blood and Shadow Warrior.
                        Whether it be ludicrous gibs or explosions, NTMAi tries its best to faithfully replicate all
                        things Build on Doom while also enhancing vanilla gameplay.
                        Your arsenal may be tough, but some enemies will have a trick or two up their sleeves...
                        <br><br>
                        NTMAi originally started off as a small project during summer 2019. It went on to
                        <a href="https://www.doomworld.com/cacowards/2020/gameplay/">win a Cacoward in 2020</a>
                        and eventually got rebooted to a much better state in early 2023.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="vr"></div>

                <div>
                    <h1>HURT ME PLENTY MORE</h1>
                    <p>
                        Want some extra challenge? NTMAi also comes with built-in
                        special support for the following WADs:
                    </p>

                    <ul>
                        <li><a href="https://www.doomworld.com/forum/topic/125461">AD MORTEM</a></li>
                        <li><a
                                href="https://www.doomworld.com/idgames/levels/doom2/Ports/megawads/dbp37_augzen">AUGER;ZENITH</a>
                        </li>
                        <li><a href="https://www.doomworld.com/idgames/levels/doom2/megawads/d64d2">Doom 64 for Doom
                                II</a></li>
                        <li><a
                                href="https://www.doomworld.com/idgames/levels/doom2/Ports/megawads/eviternity">Eviternity</a>
                        </li>
                        <li><a href="https://www.doomworld.com/idgames/levels/doom2/Ports/megawads/mayhem19">MAYhem
                                2019</a>
                        </li>
                        <li><a href="https://www.doomworld.com/idgames/?id=13600">Scythe 2</a></li>
                    </ul>

                    <p>
                        Playing these will automatically enable unique content;
                        maybe even some new weapons and monsters to play with!
                        <br><br>
                        For maximum compatibility, make sure to load NTMAi
                        <b>after</b> any of these WADs, otherwise you might get
                        weird results.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </main>

        <footer>
            <p>
                This is a non-profit fan project.
                Artwork by 3D Realms, edited by Kinsie.
                Logo by Craneo.
            </p>

            <div class="hr"></div>

            <div class="footer">
                <div class="footer-left">All content &copy; respective owners.</div>
                <div class="footer-center">Powered by <a href="/">Can't Sleep</a></div>
                <div class="footer-right" id="last-updated"></div>
            </div>
        </footer>
    </div>
</body>

</html>